document.full_text: a strong earthquake of magnitude 7.4 shook northeast and eastern japan late on thursday, and a tsunami warning was issued for the northeastern coast of japan, an area badly hit by the march 11 earthquake.
document.title: quake shakes northeastern japan, tsunami warning issued
